Illaoi's current winrate problem is similar to release Lux. When Lux came out, she had a sub 50% winrate for quite a while due to her damage being unreliable, but as players figured out how to use/build her, she worked her way up without buffs or major meta shifts.
After spending enough time on Illaoi to get to level 5 mastery, I learned how to reliably deal the most damage on my team by landing my abilities and maximizing my E windows, as well as discovering a build that enables her potential:

